WEBVTT

NOTE Captions for the PCH (Chapter 2600) persona video. Timings are approximate.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.500
Running a Pennsylvania personal care home? Chapter 2600 expects
twelve hours of training a year for every direct care worker,

2
00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:14.000
current RASP assessments and support plans, medication practicums,
Act 34 clearances, and fire drill logs — each with its own documentation.

3
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Here's the truth. Most homes don't get cited for skipping the work.

4
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000
They get cited because the sign-in sheet can't be found.

5
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:32.000
CareBase logs the hours as they happen, keeps the documentation
attached, and has Chapter 2600 mapped for you.

6
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:38.000
So you're ready long before the surveyor ever arrives.
